        <p>Aaj kal 20s and 30s mein hi white hair aana common ho gaya hai. Pollution, stress, poor diet, and lifestyle changes — ye sab premature greying ke kaaran hain. Aur sabfrom pehla reaction hota hai — hair dye lagao! Lekin chemical dyes scalp damage karte hain, allergies cause karte hain, and long-term mein baalon ko and kamzor bana dete hain.</p>

