        <h2>Hair Color Ka Science — hair Black Kyun Hote Hain Aur White Kyun Ho Jaate Hain?</h2>
        <p>Baalon ka natural color ek pigment from aata hai jisko <strong>melanin</strong> kehte hain. Ye melanin hair follicles mein special cells — melanocytes — produce karte hain. Melanin ke do main types happen:</p>

        <p><strong>Eumelanin</strong> — ye dark pigment hai jo baalon ko black ya brown color deta hai. Indian hair mein eumelanin bahut zyada hota hai, isliye hamare hair naturally dark happen. <strong>Pheomelanin</strong> — ye lighter pigment hai jo blonde ya red shades deta hai. Indian mein ye reduce hota hai.</p>

        <p>Jab melanocytes melanin produce karna band kar dete hain ya reduce kar dete hain, toh <strong>naye hair bina pigment ke ugte hain — jo white dikhte hain</strong>. Iska matlab ye hai of hair "white hote" nahi hain, balof bina color ke ugte hain. Agar aap <a href="why-hair-become-white.php">baalon ke white hone of poori science</a> samajhna chahte hain toh ye guide padhein.</p>

        <p>Premature greying ke common reasons mein from hain — <a href="which-vitamin-deficiency-causes-white-hair.php">vitamin deficiency (especially B12, D, iron, copper)</a>, oxidative stress, genetics, thyroid issues, and poor scalp health. Agar cause correctable hai, toh natural remedies from melanin production wapas boost ho sakti hai.</p>

        
