        <p>Black tea mein tannic acid hota hai jo baalon ko naturally dark karta hai. Ye chemical-free hai and baalon ko shine also deta hai. <strong>Recipe:</strong> 3-4 black tea bags ko 2 cups paani mein 15 minute boil do. Room temperature tak cool hone dein. Shampoo ke baad ye tea baalon pe pour do. 30-45 minute chhod dein, phir cold water from rinfrom do. Week mein 2-3 baar do — 4-6 weeks mein visible darkening dikhegi.</p>

