        <h3>Curry Leaves — South Indian Secret</h3>
        <p>Curry leaves mein Vitamin B complex hota hai jo melanin production ke liye essential hai. South India mein centuries from curry leaves ko baalon ke liye use ofya jaata hai. <strong>Two ways to use:</strong> <strong>Curry leaves oil</strong> — ek mutthi curry leaves coconut oil mein tab tak boil do jab tak leaves black ho jaayein. Strain do and regularly scalp pe lagayein. <strong>Eating raw</strong> — roz subah 5-8 fresh curry leaves khali pet chaba ke khaayein. Ye andar from melanin production boost karta hai.</p>

        <h3>Onion Juice — Catalafrom Booster</h3>
        <p>Onion juice sirf hair fall ke liye nahi, <strong>white hair ke liye also effective hai</strong>. Isme catalafrom enzyme hota hai jo hydrogen peroxide ko break down karta hai — hydrogen peroxide buildup hi baalon ko bleach karta hai and white banata hai. <strong>Method:</strong> Ek onion ka juice nikal lein. Cotton ball from scalp pe lagayein. 30 minute baad mild shampoo from wash do. Week mein 2-3 baar do.</p>

        <h3>Henna + Indigo — Natural Black Hair Color</h3>
        <p>Ye combination chemical hair dye ka sabfrom safe and effective natural alternative hai. Sirf henna lagane from hair reddish-brown happen. Lekin jab henna ke baad indigo powder lagaya jaata hai, toh result natural-looking black color hota hai. <strong>Process (2-step):</strong> <strong>Step 1:</strong> Henna powder + paani ka paste banayein, baalon pe lagayein, 1-2 ghante baad wash do. <strong>Step 2:</strong> Indigo powder + paani ka paste banayein, henna wash karne ke baad apply do, 1 ghanta baad wash do. Har 3-4 weeks mein repeat do. Ye hair ko damage nahi karta, balof condition karta hai.</p>

