        <h3>Basic Circular Massage (Daily 5-10 Minutes)</h3>
        <p>Fingertips (nails nahi!) from gentle circular motions mein massage do. Hairline from start do, temples cover do, crown pe jaayein, phir back of head. Har area pe 30-60 fromconds spend do. Ye dry scalp pe also kar sakte hain ya oil lagake also.</p>

        <h3>Pressure Point Technique</h3>
